sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Researcher
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant Runner as Agent Runner
    participant LLM as Backend LLM
    participant Target as Target Agent subprocess
    participant Eval as evaluate.py subprocess
    participant Ctx as Context Manager

    User->>Orch: sia --task gpqa --max_gen N
    Orch->>Orch: load task files (task.md, reference agent, sample exec)
    Orch->>Orch: create runs/run_N/ and per-run venv

    Note over Orch,LLM: Generation 1 — meta-agent bootstraps target agent
    Orch->>Runner: run meta-agent (build_meta_prompt)
    Runner->>LLM: generate target_agent.py
    LLM-->>Target: writes gen_1/target_agent.py

    loop for gen in 1..N
        Orch->>Target: run target agent (subprocess in venv or Docker)
        Target-->>Orch: agent_execution log + stdout log
        Orch->>Eval: run evaluate.py --gen-dir (if present)
        Eval-->>Orch: results.json
        Orch->>Ctx: add_generation(metrics, agent stats)
        Ctx->>Runner: LLM diff summary (gen > 1)
        alt gen < N
            Orch->>Runner: run feedback-agent (build_feedback_prompt)
            Runner->>LLM: analyze logs, rewrite agent
            LLM-->>Target: writes gen_{n+1} target_agent.py + improvement.md
        end
    end

    Orch->>Ctx: finalize() — summary statistics
    Ctx-->>User: runs/run_N/context.md
